caption: On Trans Day of Visibility, we celebrate the strength, resilience, and beauty of the trans community. Let’s amplify trans voices, honor their journeys, and champion trans authors whose words inspire, challenge, and transform the world one story at a time. A huge thank you to our fabulous hosts of Pep & Hugh’s Queer History 101 Book Club, @peppermint247 & @hughoryan , for curating this incredible list of inspiring trans authors. Together, we continue to uplift and empower the voices that need to be heard 🏳️‍⚧️
